<Game>
	<Name>JoJo no Kimyou na Bouken (Japan)</Name>
	<plot>Overview:Jojo no Kimyou na Bouken ("Jojo's Bizarre Adventure" is the official translation) is a point-and-click adventure game largely driven by menus and an RPG, in which two fighters duel via a turn-based combat system. The game follows the story of the manga, switching playable characters starting with Jotaro Kujo.Jojo no Kimyou na Bouken is the first video game adaptation of Jojo's Bizarre Adventure, and was never released outside of Japan.					</plot>
